plot: The team meets their new leader, a man known to Toby (but not in a good way). They investigate how money that is suppose to be in the evidence locker ended up in sport team's locker room.

Expecting McCluskey's promotion, the team instead finds Brian Becker as their new leader, a former cop who hasn't forgiven Toby for Det. Charlie Marks' death. Their first case together: money accidentally discovered in a football locker room that had been successfully stolen from a police evidence locker.—statmanjeff
